dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents the railroads of the world at 1:250,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. World Railroads provides a base map layer for the railroads of the world. DeLorme Publishing Company; ESRI. (2014). World Railroads, 2013. ESRI. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/kb463vw6094
